stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> Idle

    Idle --> Linking: /link XXXXXX
    Linking --> Idle: Success
    Linking --> Idle: Failure

    Idle --> Profile: /profile or "Профиль"
    Profile --> Idle

    Idle --> GenerateMenu: /generate or "Генерация"
    GenerateMenu --> WaitingFile: User selects generate
    WaitingFile --> WaitingSchema: File received
    WaitingSchema --> Generating: Schema received
    Generating --> Idle: Generation complete

    Idle --> Idle: Unlinked user tries generate -> Explain linking

    note right of Idle
        User can be linked or unlinked.
        Unlinked users see linking instructions.
    end note